metaface.server
Class VHMLFAElement

java.lang.Object
  metaface.server.VHMLFAElement
class VHMLFAElement
extends Object

This class stores a VHML Facial Animation Element for recall when rendering MPEG-4 FAPs

Version:
1.0
Author:
Simon Beard
See Also:
VHMLParser, VHMLReader
